data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful ranch style home located within Silver Peaks. This charming corner lot offers an inviting open floor plan with newer flooring throughout most the house. The large kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, stylish backsplash, cabinets that provide ample storage along with a pantry. The kitchen overlooks the beautiful living & dining area-creating a perfect space for everyday meals and or special gatherings.
The home is move in ready and offers 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths. The cozy primary bedroom includes a private bathroom with dual sinks and two closets, one being a walk-in closet with built in shelving and drawers.
Venture on to the gated backyard, you'll find a newer deck, a large grass area and a dog run. There is also an attached 2-car garage with epoxy floors and newly insulated walls.
You will find many playgrounds and an elementary school nestled in this beautiful development.
This home is a fantastic opportunity to enjoy a comfortable & contemporary lifestyle here.  
Contact us today to check out your new home!!
Buyers are offering $3,000 in concessions to go to closing costs. Don't let this gem pass you by!
